+# Shipshape Rigging
+
+## Stack
+- language: JavaScript
+- runtime: Node.js
+- packageManager: npm
+
+## Directories
+- implementation: src
+- specs: features
+- verification: features/support
+- assets: data
+- scantlings: none
+
+## Commands
+- discover: `npx cucumber-js --dry-run --format usage`
+- focused: `npx cucumber-js --tags '@focus'`
+- broad: `npx cucumber-js`
+- coverage: `npx cucumber-js`
+- step-usage: `npx cucumber-js --format usage-json`
+- plank-inventory: `none`
+- typecheck: `none`
+- lint: `none`
+
+## Perturbation
+- message: "PERTURBATION: This is a test perturbation to verify the system works"
+- perturb: `// PERTURBATION: `
+
+## Tiers
+- default: @logic
+- sandbox: none
+- policy: none
+- budget: none
+- weather: none
+- runrecord: none
+
+## Dependencies
+- policy: locked
+- dependency: @cucumber/cucumber
+
+## Outbound
+- outbound: none
+- ship: none
+- verify: none
\ No newline at end of file
